HEADWORD: Stultiloquent
<hw>Stul*til"o*quent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. L.
<ets>stultiloquus</ets>. See <er>Stultiloquence</er>.]</ety> <def>Given
to, or characterized by, silly talk; babbling.</def> --
